Showcasing 25 years as an illustrator. Over this time I have completed 2,984 mainstream interior pages. This does not include Indy projects. Featured today is Carnage #1 all digitally painted. This book has three covers. One of the covers is an interior page @marvel selected for a variant. I enjoyed this illustrating this book as I had creative freedom to design panels and outline the story before the writer was involved. The story maintained about 80% of my outline. Being that I had more influence I put more effort in making Carnage more glossy and alien in appearance.
